<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عنْ زَيدِ بنِ أَرقَمَ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رَوَى عَنهُ فِراسٌ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٩٤٦٩]</span> عَتّابُ بنُ هُرْمُزَ <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>سَمِعَ أَنَسًا <span class="c2">(٦)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>رَوى عَنهُ شُعْبَةُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٩٤٧٠]</span> عَتّابُ بنُ حَربٍ، المُزنِيُّ <span class="c2">(٧)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>سَمِعَ صالِحَ بنَ رُسْتُم.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>سَمِعَ مِنهُ عَمْرُو بنُ عَلِيٍّ، وضعَّفَه جِدًّا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>في البَصْريّينَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٩٤٧١]</span> عَتّابُ بنُ سِماكٍ،<span class="c5"> وَيُقالُ:</span> ابنُ مُزيْلم بنِ قربا، النَّخَعِيُّ <span class="c2">(٨)</span> <span class="c2">(٩)</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>سَمَعَ إبْراهيمَ، قَولَهُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
